      "writtenOn": "2016-03-16T23:48:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Technically the field in task_struct is called \"no_new_privs\", PR_GET_NO_NEW_PRIVS is the prctl() option. So I would say the same thing the help says,\n\n\"Set \\fBno_new_privs\\fB. ...\"",
