      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-03-16T23:54:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "But we only \"set\" this by calling a system call, not by setting that bit directly in the task_struct. The help description is very much non-helpful (i.e., \"no_new_privs\" means nothing without more context), so it needs something more in my opinion, as an unfamiliar reader. Do you have a more informative explanation to propose?",
